    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ornamental receptacles on an elevated stand, used for growing plants and flowers, sometimes having a lead-lined top. For receptacles not associated with a stand, use "jardinières (containers)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
